content:
Product and Category Record Pages Have a New Layout

Easily review essential product and category information and navigate through related details with the new, intuitive layout. All customers automatically receive the refreshed default layouts. You can also customize the product and category layouts in the Lightning App Builder.

Where: This change applies to B2B and D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: View record information in the main region of the page (1). Expanded cards for related quick links (2) are pinned on the right side. Use the tabs to access more features (3).

SEE ALSO
Salesforce Help: Create Page Layouts 
Salesforce Help: Assign Page Layouts to Profiles or Record Types
title: Product and Category Record Pages Updated
